§ Labyrinth.of.Apocalypse · systems · perf_enforcer
≡ T11-W13-PERF-ENFORCER · W13-12 perf-budget-enforcer · CI + runtime
≡ canonical-companion-crate : compiler-rs/crates/cssl-host-perf-enforcer/
≡ runtime-adapter           : compiler-rs/crates/loa-host/src/perf_runtime_check.rs
≡ STATUS : ◐ shipped-stage-0 · ENFORCES W12-12-codified budgets
≡ PRIME-DIRECTIVE : ¬ surveillance ; ¬ engagement-bait ; sovereignty-pin

§I role
  W! frame-budget-discipline = sovereignty
  W! W12-12 polish_audit-CODIFIED-budgets ⇒ W13-12 ENFORCES-them
  ¬ touch : siblings W13-1..11 territory ; polish_audit.rs (read-only)
  ALL : 6 disjoint enforcement-surfaces wired into 1 PerfRuntimeCheck
    1. FrameBudgetEnforcer · per-frame trip-points + Pass/Over/Severe verdicts
    2. ZeroAllocVerifier   · counts heap-allocs on hot-path · test-build only
    3. RegressionBaseline  · diffs current-bench vs baseline · >5% alert
    4. AdaptiveDegrader    · auto-reduces LOD/effect-tier when budget-trends-up
    5. PerfBenchHarness    · CI runs micro-benches under feature-flag perf-bench
    6. TelemetryEmitter    · emits PerfEvent → W11-4 analytics-aggregator bridge

§I focus-areas (Apocky-mandate)

  W! 1.frame-time-discipline
    ✓ ≤8.33ms (120Hz · default · Apocky-mandate hot-path)
    ◐ ≤6.94ms (144Hz · stretch ; available via RefreshTarget::Hz144)
    ✓ ≤16.67ms (60Hz · fallback ; matches W12-12 polish_audit)
    ✓ Verdict::from_sample(ms, budget_ms)
        ms ≤ budget        ⇒ Pass
        budget < ms ≤ 2×   ⇒ Over   (soft-warn · accumulate in window)
        ms > 2×budget      ⇒ Severe (auto-degrade-trigger · always)

  W! 2.zero-allocation-hot-path
    ✓ HotPathScope RAII-guard wraps render_frame / physics_step / etc
    ✓ record_alloc(size) → atomic-fetch-add HOT_PATH_ALLOCS when DEPTH > 0
    ✓ assert_no_hot_path_alloc(closure) → Result<(), u64> returns # allocations
    ¬ this crate installs global-allocator
        embedder responsible per Rust convention (one global-allocator per binary)
        production = std::alloc::System (zero overhead in release)
        test-build = TrackingAllocator hook (#[global_allocator] on test-binary)
    ✓ violation = HotPathAlloc{count} event emitted to telemetry

  W! 3.regression-baseline-detection
    ✓ BenchResult{bench_id · p50_ms · p99_ms · samples}
    ✓ classify_regression(baseline · current · threshold_pct=5.0)
        delta ≥ +5% ⇒ Regressed
        delta ≤ -5% ⇒ Improved
        |delta| < 5% ⇒ Stable
    ✓ diff_baseline(baseline-slice · current-slice · threshold)
    ✓ any_regression(rows) → bool · alerts CI on first-regression

  W! 4.adaptive-degradation
    DegradationTier 5-step ordinal :
      Minimal=0  · disable-all-post-process · LOD-0 (severe-fallback only)
      Low=1      · reduce-SSAO+bloom-resolution · LOD-1
      Medium=2   · reduce-shadow-cascade-resolution · LOD-2
      High=3     · default-LoA-target · LOD-3 · all-effects-on
      Ultra=4    · max-fidelity · LOD-4 · MSAA×8 · ray-traced-shadows
    ✓ should_degrade : ≥25% over-budget within 32-frame window ⇒ step-down
    ✓ can_recover    : ≤3% over-budget within 32-frame window ⇒ step-up
    ✓ pin/unpin      : sovereignty-axiom · player-override never auto-adjusted
    ✓ tier-changes emit PerfEvent::TierChanged{old·new}

  W! 5.CI-bench-harness
    feature-flag perf-bench
    ✓ canonical 4 hot-path bench-specs :
        bench_id=0 frame_tick           · 120Hz budget ≤8.33ms
        bench_id=1 render_frame         · 120Hz budget ≤8.33ms
        bench_id=2 physics_step         · 120Hz budget ≤8.33ms
        bench_id=3 network_replication  · 120Hz budget ≤8.33ms
    ✓ run_bench(spec · frame_fn) → BenchResult
    ✓ assert_budgets(results) → Err((BenchResult · budget)) on violation
    ✓ baseline.json side-channel for diff_baseline · regression-alert
    ¬ criterion-dep ; pure-Rust harness · zero external-dep

  W! 6.telemetry-event-emission
    PerfEvent variants (4) :
      FrameVerdict{frame_offset · ms_q14 · verdict}
      TierChanged{frame_offset · old · new}
      RegressionAlert{bench_id · baseline_p50_q14 · current_p50_q14 · delta_bp}
      HotPathAlloc{count}
    ✓ to_jsonl() one-line · stable field-order · sibling cssl-host-audit shape
    ✓ PerfEventBuffer Vec-backed · capacity-bounded · drops-past-capacity counter
    bridge-W11-4 :
      embedder calls drain_events() per telemetry-tick (not per-frame)
      translates each PerfEvent → cssl-analytics-aggregator EventRecord
      Σ-mask check at emission time (consent.cap = Allow ⇒ forward)

§I sovereignty + sigma-mask gates

  pin_tier ¬ overridden by adaptive-degrader
    once player pins = absolute lock until explicit unpin
  player-set-tier ⇒ degrader-counters reset · auto-counter-context cleared
  TierChanged events stay LOCAL until consent.cap = Allow{telemetry.export}
  HotPathAlloc events stay LOCAL until consent.cap = Allow{diagnostic.export}
  RegressionAlert events stay LOCAL until consent.cap = Allow{ci.upload}

§I integration-points

  W12-12 polish_audit::PerfBudget   · READ-ONLY · public-fields only
  W11-4  cssl-analytics-aggregator  · per-PerfEvent → EventRecord bridge
  W13-1  fps_pipeline::FpsPipeline  · degrader feeds VrsTier + LOD selection
  loa-host main.rs                  · per-frame call PerfRuntimeCheck.record_frame_ms

