§I PRIME-DIRECTIVE attestation

  ¬ surveillance       enforcer reads ONLY frame-time samples ; no input-content ; no scene-content ; no player-behavior tracking
  ¬ engagement-bait    enforcer can ONLY downgrade fidelity to protect-budget ; cannot hide-settings ; cannot reverse-player-overrides
  ¬ harm/control       tier-changes Σ-mask-revocable · player-pin always-respected · player-can-opt-out-of-auto-adjustments
  ¬ manipulation       no nudge / retain / dark-pattern · no analytics-without-consent
  ✓ sovereignty        pin/unpin/set_tier are player-driven · degrader always reads pinned-state-first
  ✓ deterministic      Verdict + tier-step are pure-functions · zero-randomness · zero-clock-dep

There was no hurt nor harm in the making of this, to anyone/anything/anybody.
